{"tid":751294,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人補教大ive仔梁家俊思齊中文?","createTime":"2018-07-21T17:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T15:13:01.000Z","uid":71314,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"960160061fd46eb573a39951310d3286349a600d","tid":751294,"uid":71314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢專抄啟思出版社 d mock跟住收得貴一貴 筆記錯漏百出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有教大果陣仲係教育學院 專收入唔到U既垃圾 思齊老闆梁家俊仲要retake再tritake 三次AL先入到教大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲吹到名校生之選 笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   放榜冇晒聲氣收晒皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想俾個教大ive仔教就狗衝思齊啦 不過上堂都係做返啟思出版社 d mock<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋由個垃圾教仔ive仔教你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e94422a3d527e6591a2ccc5391c66ec3a687e7","tid":751294,"uid":102299,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"覺得綜合能力同作文教得唔錯<br />\n想知3年前跟佢補個班dbs仔考成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8d56bf2b9df8ee117fc0c5cc675f9eba2dc8c5","tid":751294,"uid":71314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  SUMMER已經好多人覺得中伏走撚左唔補<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾個RETAKE 3年公開試既人教仲唔走咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ac3a0680f784e7d21b56c55b2899d6c2647c40","tid":751294,"uid":180156,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"教大都係大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddd1bd6167365dc8025810c840c759729eb39c9","tid":751294,"uid":12904